### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Echo GET request with query params
GET http://localhost:3000/echo?foo=bar&baz=qux

### Echo POST request with body
POST http://localhost:3000/echo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Hello World",
  "data": [1, 2, 3]
}

### Get all received headers
GET http://localhost:3000/api/headers
X-Custom-Header: custom-value
X-Request-ID: 12345

### Test JSON parsing
POST http://localhost:3000/api/json
